metadata.name: WoWG Derivative #21816
metadata.description:
Created by Katalina-Ooma [Artstation](https://www.artstation.com/katalina_ooma)

A derivative art piece representing [WoWG lady #21816](https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0xf61f24c2d93bf2de187546b14425bf631f28d6dc/21816/) from the special World of Women Galaxy verified collection. Designed and produced in Clip Studio Paint Pro & Adobe Photoshop.

A [Timelapse Creation Video](https://vimeo.com/743688746) is also provided. Music: 'Atmospheric Ambient Electronic Music'
